        <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Class" xmi:id="_tWvYIHyjEeyqPtdb1vr-DA" name="ASimpleShape" isAbstract="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:id="_tYPM8HyjEeyqPtdb1vr-DA">
            <body>&#xD;
@author charlielockyer&#xD;
An abstract class describing an abstract simple shape on a 2D plane, like a screen&#xD;
A simple shape has its own custom painting instructions, and is not composed of other shapes&#xD;
Simple shapes are the most basic shapes and inherently have a color</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <generalization xmi:id="_tXmTwHyjEeyqPtdb1vr-DA" general="_tWkZAHyjEeyqPtdb1vr-DA"/>
